  "markup": "Join Dr\u0026rsquo;s. Christopher Carraway and Brian Fitzpatrick for an informative low level laser session designed with the Athlete in mind, with a focus on Running. \u003Cbr /\u003E\nTopics to be discussed: \u003Cbr /\u003E\nLaser Treatments to improve performance - Preconditioning, Mid Run, and Post Run \u003Cbr /\u003E\nProper management of common Running injuries and challenges."
